<p class="ql-align-justify"> 2：确定轮廓，重线定位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/4189fc6836094803aec588cd12e64247.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 3：整体调整布局，分出轻重笔触，添加配饰以增加龙之气韵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200921/706369b4646842fcac17b4a0a178b8dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
